text: The Nokia 3.2 is a Nokia-branded entry-level smartphone released 21 May 2019 running the Android operating system. == Models == The phone comes in 2 models: one with 2 GB RAM and 16 GB storage, and another more expensive model, with 3 GB RAM and 32 GB storage. == Design == The phone has a plastic body. It has dual sim support and a screen to body ratio of ~80.5% == Reference List == Category:Nokia Category:Android (operating system) devices Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2019
title: Nokia 3.2
